FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1776438666
OL,3,CGlyn Razzell: Murderer who refuses to
OL,4,Csay where wife's body is granted parole
OL,6,FRazzell has previously appeared before
OL,7,Fthe Parole Board and been unsuccessful.
OL,9,FHowever, a spokesperson for the board
OL,10,Fsaid this most recent decision was
OL,11,Fmade "focused on what risk a prisoner
OL,12,Fcould represent to the public if
OL,13,Freleased and whether that risk is
OL,14,Fmanageable in the community".
OL,16,FRazzell and his wife were embroiled in
OL,17,Fdivorce proceedings when she went
OL,18,Fmissing and his trial was told he
OL,19,Ffaced a financial settlement he was
OL,20,Fnot prepared to accept.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1776438666
OL,3,CGlyn Razzell: Murderer who refuses to
OL,4,Csay where wife's body is granted parole
OL,6,FDuring the trial, the court heard how
OL,7,FMrs Razzell, originally from
OL,8,FCarmarthen, left her home in the
OL,9,Fvillage of Highworth, near Swindon, at
OL,10,F8.45am on 19 March 2002 with her
OL,11,Fchildren and boyfriend Greg Worrall.
OL,13,FShe dropped off her boyfriend in
OL,14,FHighworth and her children at school
OL,15,Fbefore being seen parking for work in
OL,16,FAlvescot Road, as usual.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1776438666
OL,3,CGlyn Razzell: Murderer who refuses to
OL,4,Csay where wife's body is granted parole
OL,6,FShe is believed to have taken her
OL,7,Fusual route down an alleyway towards
OL,8,Fthe college and her phone was found in
OL,9,Fa recess of the alleyway the next day
OL,10,Fduring a police search.
OL,12,FHer boyfriend contacted police on the
OL,13,Fevening of her disappearance after she
OL,14,Ffailed to pick up her children from
OL,15,Ftheir after-school club. Glyn Razzell
OL,16,Fhas always denied killing her.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
